<article class="card h-100 shadow-sm product-card">
  <img
    src="{{image}}"
    class="card-img-top object-fit-cover"
    alt="{{name}}"
    width="400"
    height="240"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
    <h2 class="h5 card-title">{{name}}</h2>
    <p class="card-text text-muted small flex-grow-1 mb-3">Артикул и краткое описание можно передать тем же способом.</p>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mt-auto gap-2">
      <span class="fw-semibold text-primary">{{price}}&nbsp;₽</span>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">В корзину</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
